OL,3,CPolanksi claims Labour in Wales are
OL,4,C'finished' ahead of the Senedd election
OL,6,FThe leader of the Green Party has
OL,7,Fclaimed that Labour's dominance of
OL,8,FWelsh politics is at an end.
OL,10,FSpeaking in Cardiff, Zack Polanski
OL,11,Ftold party members that voters are
OL,12,Fdeserting Labour in favour of a "new
OL,13,Fdirection" for Wales.
OL,15,F"Labour is finished; they are done,"
OL,16,FMr Polanski said. "We know that people
OL,17,Fare looking for something different,
OL,18,Fso it is increasingly looking like
OL,19,FPlaid will do very well in Wales and
OL,20,Fwill likely be the largest party."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
