OL,3,CPolanksi claims Labour in Wales are
OL,4,C'finished' ahead of the Senedd election
OL,6,FMr Polanski argued that a Green
OL,7,Fpresence in the Senedd would be vital
OL,8,Ffor holding Plaid to account.
OL,10,F"The question is: what can the Green
OL,11,FParty offer in holding them to
OL,12,Faccount?" he asked. "We want to make
OL,13,Fsure we are at the table bringing
OL,14,Fthings like a rent freeze, because
OL,15,Fpeople's bills are far too high, and
OL,16,Fbringing water into public hands."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
