OL,3,CPolanksi claims Labour in Wales are
OL,4,C'finished' ahead of the Senedd election
OL,6,FHe added that it was "outrageous" that
OL,7,Fwater companies continue to pump
OL,8,Fsewage into Welsh waterways while
OL,9,Fincreasing bills, and reiterated Green
OL,10,Fpledges to abolish council tax in
OL,11,Ffavour of a "much fairer system."
OL,13,FRecent polling by ITV Cymru Wales
OL,14,Fshowed that for the first time ever,
OL,15,Fthe Green Party is polling in third
OL,16,Fplace at 13%, with Labour in fourth -
OL,17,Fits lowest ever point -at 10%
OL,18,Falongside the Conservatives.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
