OL,3,CPolanksi claims Labour in Wales are
OL,4,C'finished' ahead of the Senedd election
OL,6,FWhilst Plaid Cymru remains ahead of
OL,7,FReform UK as the predicted largest
OL,8,Fparty in the upcoming Senedd election,
OL,9,Faccording to the first poll of 2026
OL,10,Ffrom ITV Cymru Wales.
